Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so rude up until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have meetings from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll write the names, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W—What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.82,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody kept calling me a genius, \Nso I guess I got a bit conceited.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.60,0:00:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do all that, it'd sure \Ntake a load off my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up and becoming the best \Nwriter in Jack won't be just a dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The early results for chapter three have you in—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.09,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,third!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.25,0:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better than chapter two.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter three is better?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we were wrong, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We helped him make chapter five even better
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and got him to start having \Nmeetings and writing names.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.10,0:00:46.94,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the most \Npopular mangaka out there!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.73,0:00:46.28,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he got Eiji to start writing names.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I've come this far for Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.37,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to learn something before I go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:56.91,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you see the blue bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:56.91,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,aozora tobikau Blue Bird
