Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,C—C—C—Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.53,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow's Holy Sword!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.16,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The most popular mangaka, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I become the most popular mangaka in Jack,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,please give me the power to \Nend one series I don't like.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.97,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Making him first is supposed to be my job—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.55,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to cross that \Nbridge when we come to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Last two!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A—Alright then, I'll come by \Ntomorrow at five to pick up the chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have a meeting after that, alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back tomorrow at five.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,R—Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei only has two pages left to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yujiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask you something.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.16,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.83,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The order manga show up in Jack \Nis the popularity order, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in the exact order, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not including gag manga, the popular \Nmanga tends to be toward the front,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,while the less popular series are in the back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you do it that way?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Most other magazines do it \Nthe same way, don't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say, I think it's unfair.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're in order of popularity, the readers will \Nknow which are popular and which aren't beforehand.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably a lot of kids out there who \Nonly read what they know everybody else likes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be fairer to rotate the order every week.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.03,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying, Fukuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That should change the questionnaire \Nresults at least a little as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The order the series appear in \Nis creating a gap in the results
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you keep your mouth shut \Nuntil you've actually been serialized!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just hear me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm just stating my opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.01,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I also don't like that whether a manga is popular \Nor gets axed is based solely on the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that like saying the editing department
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.18,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't able to judge whether or not \Na manga is interesting on their own?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be saying that in the \Nediting department if I were you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm a nice guy, so I'll \Nlisten to what you have to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, please listen to this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In Jack, if you don't have a flashy \Nchapter one with an exciting climax,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you're on the fast track to getting cancelled.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst case, a series can be cancelled \Ndepending on its chapter three results.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.29,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, writers are afraid to write a manga that \Nstarts out simple and gradually gets more interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes all the new \Nseries you see feel the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the editing department should \Nhave a bit more faith in new series
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and at least let them run until \Nthe first volume comes out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we gave all the new series that much leeway,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd only be able to run about \Nfive new series every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.64,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think there are manga out there that \Nhave potential to get better over time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a main character who starts \Nreally weak, but gradually gets better.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With the current system, a series like that\N would never be popular from the get-go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but even for a series like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it just has to have a good \Nenough hook to not get cancelled.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you writing a series like that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.46,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing a name where the main \Ncharacter starts out as a winner.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it just sounds like you're asking for
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.97,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,special treatment in case your series \Ndoesn't do well in the beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.97,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to argue about \Nhow the magazine is set up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the editing department's job.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You just focus on writing your manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda-sensei!!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the part about rotating the order.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And sounds fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.53,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even thought about that before.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to you, it sounds like too \Nmuch is based on the questionnaire.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't good for manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the end of manga if the authors \Nare only writing to get more votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.38,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite series in Jack is "To Love-Ru."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.34,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely at a \Ndisadvantage in the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little ecchi,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so nobody wants anybody else to know \Nthat they picked it as one of the top three.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I was too afraid to choose \N"Ichigo 100%" on the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.86,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He submitted the questionnaires?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.86,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are grade schoolers out there who have their parents send their questionnaire in.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too embarrassing to choose "To Love-Ru!"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's because they're ecchi, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.42,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"To Love-Ru" is a shounen manga
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for real men, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know exactly what you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure they're taking that into account.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets center color pages every once in a while
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the volumes seem to sell pretty well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The volumes are selling well, so \Nit should get more color pages!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.52,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's good for the \Nmagazine's image to have so many ecchi—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecchi drawings and panty shots \Nare what define a shounen manga!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're every guy's dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"We are going to change Jack."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand what you meant now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ideas are really interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other thoughts?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think the contents \Nof the stories should change,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.50,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but first, rotate the cover \Npage and the series order.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, on the inside of the cover,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,add a fold out swimsuit poster of an idol.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.05,0:07:27.88,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just something you want to see!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the other magazines do it, so Jack should too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You need an idol in a magazine made for guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mark of pride that Jack doesn't \Nneed tricks or models to sell magazines!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs to be proud of \Nsomething stupid like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.09,0:07:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you guys save it until \Nafter we finish this chapter?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be finished by tomorrow, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do you have?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm already finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you think it will take you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The backgrounds are amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I said so, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai's technique is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Since coming here,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned the most from watching Nakai work.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to flatter me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and do the inking, \Nwhiteout, and screentones.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.27,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I can leave the rest up to you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You going to sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you won't wake up until \NYujiro comes tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets here, you'll have your next meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.49,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably think about where you \Nwant the story to go next before you fall asleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have just woken up, so if I don't do that,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be too easily persuaded.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll give it some thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.05,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,adding
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,another ally
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I said I'd only help out with chapter five.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A new ally it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Notebook, notebook—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that notebook?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Notebook, notebook—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Notebook?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.79,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very important notebook, \Nso I put it in my desk drawer.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I need one who can fly—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.63,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that one from the sparrow \Nmanga I wrote back in 4th grade.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, is that a list of characters?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been drawing manga ever \Nsince I started grade school,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so there are a lot of characters I can use.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My house in Aomori was really \Nin the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.16,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of my classmates lived \Nat least half an hour away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.66,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They all played games and stuff \Nto keep themselves occupied.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the closest game stores were pretty far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't have much money anyway,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just drew manga all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always liked doing that best anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess most people \Nwho decide to be mangakas
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,have been doodling in \Nnotebooks since they were kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably think they're \Ngood enough to make it big.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's how it was for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Crow was a character I \Ncame up with in grade school.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Grade school—
