Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:50.04,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are the burning energy that resides in you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.87,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Hero Kimi no Naka ni Aru
