Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:56.59,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Through some turn of events, you've been driven up against a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:56.59,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Douiu Wakedaka Dai Pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:03.39,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,But do not fret or worry, and put on a big, bright smile
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.63,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Sonna Toki Koso
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.39,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Waratte Miro yo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:09.35,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take on the foes who stand before you, no matter how big they are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:09.35,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na Aite ni Tachimukae
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:16.07,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, muster your strength, and charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:16.07,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Sou sa Ima, Hashiridasun da
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.32,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's smile—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.32,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Minna no Egao o
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.53,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially her smile—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.53,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Ano Ko no Egao o
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:30.25,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gives me the endless power I need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:30.25,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Omoeba Minagiru Mugen no Power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.67,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are the legends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.67,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Hero Sore ga Densetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.75,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are super cool
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.75,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Hero Totemo Kakkoii
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:44.51,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are the burning energy that resides in you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.34,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,Hero Kimi no Naka ni Aru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.51,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Atsui Energy
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, it started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.89,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,The burning energy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.89,OP-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Moeru Energy
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your drawings are so good.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.69,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.03,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Up until my uncle died, I \Nwas always drawing manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.45,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,At home and even at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It was so fun
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.95,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,that I lost all track of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.40,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I got so absorbed in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loved manga since I was a kid
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and always wanted to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.76,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I should have something that \Neven Shuujin would want to write.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit sudden, but is it \Nalright if I quit as your assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.14,0:12:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you figured something out?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stop here and go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't just quit in \Nthe middle of something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave after we're finished with chapter five.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped come up with this one, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can keep up with Niizuma \Nwithout anybody's help.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda, you can quit \Nwhenever you want to, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you here all by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stick around to help \Nat least until I get serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure and get serialized myself, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.47,0:13:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to become a mangaka is \Na little will-power and a lot of persistence.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure and get serialized, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be in Jack with everyone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's finish this up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.48,Plate,,0,0,0,,{\fs33.426\frz-19.5\fax0.35\blur0.869\pos(440,187.185)\c&H2F1807&}Takagi
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels the same no matter what I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you make it too original, \Nit isn't mainstream anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, Azuki's anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:20.04,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,We are all holding a ticket to bright, sparkling days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.63,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,And a ribbon that—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Azuki'll be in this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She only had a few lines last week.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"St. Viz Girls?"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.91,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to work early tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have tomorrow off.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Record that for me, will ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter five, 19 pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work everybody.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Yujiro, let's have our meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.18,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't here for very long,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was short, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked you to stick \Naround at least another couple weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need three assistants.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed on my own up until the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Two assistants is plenty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like there's something \Ndifferent about you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be writing a name \Nsoon, so please take a look at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.16,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,There's something obviously different about him.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess most people \Nwho decide to be mangakas
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.49,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have been doodling in \Nnotebooks since they were kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Crow was a character I \Ncame up with in grade school.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,My dream from back then \Nof becoming a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The characters I loved back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.02,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I know there's one.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.77,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,A character whose story \Nwould be perfect for Shuujin to write.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just have to wait and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that exciting?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My room's on the third floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of my parents are at work \Nand my brother's still at practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.90,0:16:14.12,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've been in a \Ngirl's house since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.67,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I—It's even more girlish \Nthan I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an email from an \Nonline cellphone novel publisher.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Miss Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have received your story "Love Apart."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.95,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and would love to publish \Nany further work on our website.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.43,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on popularity, we may also \Nmake it available for mobile distribution.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}was{\i0} the one who wrote it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Saiko and Azuki were the models, \Nso I guess it was really easy to write.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi-sensei,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,please write more for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still got a name to write.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was all you wanted me to see,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you just forward it to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to surprise you
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and celebrate with you, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you just come to my house?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But your brother is there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is summer break.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's got the day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, but I'm only going to help out a little!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to write it all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard trying to \Ncome up with a battle story.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a manga writer.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can write your scenario here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even use my computer.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, stay and write here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave before my parents come home!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, you win.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna close your mail, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the submission page.
