Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's grandpa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the hot springs \Nwith Takayama next door.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.15,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but here's some money.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that with what I've made so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure and pay back \Neverything I've borrowed so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.00,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There're a lot, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,These are really bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember them being better than this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a story about becoming the \Nbest suspicious-looking guy in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember there being something in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an idea for a shady detective \Nand wrote it in a different notebook.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,352)\frz65\fs36\b1\c&HE6EDEF&\blur1.003}Con Detective Hikake
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,352)\frz65\fs36\b1\bord1.671\blur1.003\c&H707173&\3c&H707173&}Con Detective Hikake
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.90,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,He's a con artist who tricks criminals into
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.64,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,exposing themselves in dead-end cases.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.80,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Most of the books at Shuujin's were manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but he had some detective novels, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.51,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We were talking about doing a battle manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.44,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but detective manga are really \Npopular in shounen magazines, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.40,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin can do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.47,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And he'll probably be great at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.77,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme the phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell him the news.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.89,0:19:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.20,0:19:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She got an email from a \Npublisher asking her to write more.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you and Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you watch "St. Viz Girls" last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki said she wasn't in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People were saying online that \Nthey wanted to see more of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just a matter of \Ntime before she gets popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.05,0:20:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Miyoshi's.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, that line's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to say this, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you with Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I like her, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you can't write anything if \Nyou're always distracted, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working hard every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With Miyoshi at her house?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal to want to spend time \Nwith the person you like, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Azuki are the strange ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.85,0:20:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's already August.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll really be done by the end of the break?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.31,0:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know when I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.26,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even I—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:15.92,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even I—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.22,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Even I want to be with Azuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:37.60,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1890)\pos(713.333,16.713)\blur1.136\fs66.852\c&H4E4844&}Mashiro Moritaka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:37.60,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1890)\pos(776.667,150.417)\blur1.136\fs56.156\c&H514D4D&}I have a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:37.60,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1890)\pos(453.333,381.056)\blur1.136\fs51.476\c&H68676E&}Azuki, please don't get mad, but\Nwhy are you okay with not seeing me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She is starting to get more popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.26,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Azuki—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It feels like she's getting \Nfurther and further away.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.14,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin as well—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.72,0:22:06.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,along with Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.56,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\frz-63\fscy80\fs36.769\b1\blur1.003\fax0.49\pos(506.667,190.528)\c&H415A5C&}You have one unread message
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:25.69,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\move(786.667,10.028,786.667,-118.328)\blur1.136\fs80.222\c&H665B54&}Azuki Miho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:25.69,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\move(646.667,127.019,646.667,-1.337)\blur1.136\fs80.222\c&H89827F&}Good Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:25.69,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\move(825.333,367.685,825.333,239.33)\fscx95\blur1.136\fs26.741\c&H5D5D5D&}It's because I want to treasure the\Npromise we made. If we wait until\Nour dream to meet comes true,\Nour joy and love will be even greater.
